  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ace Squared is a multiplayer arena first-person shooter. You can build huge structures and dig tunnels behind enemy lines. Imagination is the only limit. Featuring 32-player servers and different gamemodes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MODIFIABLE WORLD</strong> - The world is fully modifiable! Build and destroy structures, and build them back again! Dig tunnels behind enemy lines and collapse their bunkers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEMODES</strong> - Includes different gamemodes. Fight other team against kills or steal the enemy flag! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COMMUNITY SERVERS</strong> - Host community servers with your own configuration as you see fit.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MODDING SUPPORT</strong> - Create your own mods and configure your server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Free</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the classic mode for FREE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot with mortars, set enemies to fire with flamethrower, capture flags by playing as a team.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/558cc0ce45ac9ec6911fccbd24df1355.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/558cc0ce45ac9ec6911fccbd24df1355.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock full game with DLC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the game in any of the many modes using DLC classes such as «Zombie», «Team Death Match» and «Capture The Flag».<br><br>We’ve got a hero for every playstyle and skill level:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Commando</strong>. A towering powerhouse armed with a minigun and a rocket launcher. Perfect for players who enjoy crushing enemies with raw force. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/1acff67f66e04ba712b676a04f2c44fa.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/1acff67f66e04ba712b676a04f2c44fa.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engineer</strong>. True to the classics, deploys turrets and soars with a jetpack. Support your team or push forward aggressively.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/90d46fd8aaf975d382a6c9f859c1b75a.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/90d46fd8aaf975d382a6c9f859c1b75a.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sniper</strong>. Land precise headshots and control key areas of the map from long range.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/742d26b9f280540dadf00f70b43ee69d.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/742d26b9f280540dadf00f70b43ee69d.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Miner</strong>. Carve tunnels, level structures, and tear through opponents with close-range firepower.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/579a2c1467a95eaac278f44b684a6ed9.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/579a2c1467a95eaac278f44b684a6ed9.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ace Squared is a multiplayer arena first-person shooter. You can build huge structures and dig tunnels behind enemy lines. Imagination is the only limit. Featuring 32-player servers and different gamemodes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MODIFIABLE WORLD</strong> - The world is fully modifiable! Build and destroy structures, and build them back again! Dig tunnels behind enemy lines and collapse their bunkers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAMEMODES</strong> - Includes different gamemodes. Fight other team against kills or steal the enemy flag! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>COMMUNITY SERVERS</strong> - Host community servers with your own configuration as you see fit.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MODDING SUPPORT</strong> - Create your own mods and configure your server!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Free</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the classic mode for FREE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot with mortars, set enemies to fire with flamethrower, capture flags by playing as a team.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/558cc0ce45ac9ec6911fccbd24df1355.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/558cc0ce45ac9ec6911fccbd24df1355.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock full game with DLC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the game in any of the many modes using DLC classes such as «Zombie», «Team Death Match» and «Capture The Flag».<br><br>We’ve got a hero for every playstyle and skill level:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Commando</strong>. A towering powerhouse armed with a minigun and a rocket launcher. Perfect for players who enjoy crushing enemies with raw force. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/1acff67f66e04ba712b676a04f2c44fa.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/1acff67f66e04ba712b676a04f2c44fa.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engineer</strong>. True to the classics, deploys turrets and soars with a jetpack. Support your team or push forward aggressively.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/90d46fd8aaf975d382a6c9f859c1b75a.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/90d46fd8aaf975d382a6c9f859c1b75a.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sniper</strong>. Land precise headshots and control key areas of the map from long range.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/742d26b9f280540dadf00f70b43ee69d.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/742d26b9f280540dadf00f70b43ee69d.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Miner</strong>. Carve tunnels, level structures, and tear through opponents with close-range firepower.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras/579a2c1467a95eaac278f44b684a6ed9.avif?t=1774460162\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151710/extras_big/579a2c1467a95eaac278f44b684a6ed9.webp?t=1774460162 width=1560 height=518 /></span></p>",
